&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Drive and oversee IT, AV and network infrastructure components of the build-out&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Coordinate with vendors onsite to manage any office move logistics&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Track schedules, deliverables, budgets and risks; &amp;amp; provide structured weekly updates&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Oversee meeting room and event space technology fit-outs&lt;/li&gt;
