&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;ESSENTIAL:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Degree in Computer Science, Electrical Engineering, AV Technology, or a related field.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Strong programming skills in SIMPL, SIMPL#, LUA** and C#.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Familiarity with Java, HTML5, and JavaScript for user interface development.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Passion for learning and a strong problem-solving mindset.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Excellent communication and teamwork skills.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Willingness to travel occasionally for system commissioning and support.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
