&lt;li&gt;Respond to emergency situations during or after hours to resolve immediate client concerns and meet service level agreements (SLAs).&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Escalate complex technical issues to senior team members as needed.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Conduct Service Swaps of live networking devices.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
